   CHINA-ARMS (Beijing) _ China's chief arms negotiator, in an
interview, says that an American proposal to build an anti-missile
defensive shield poses an unacceptable threat to China's security
and could force it to significantly expand its own nuclear forces
in response. By Erik Eckholm.
