   JOEMURRAY-COLUMN _ LUFKIN, Texas _ A fellow I know who is moving
across the country sent his wife on ahead to find them a house.
When I talked with him the other day, his wife had called to tell
him she had found them a house. Not just any house, but absolutely
the very house that he's always wanted _ you know, with the
upgraded kitchen counter tops and all. (Murray, Cox News Service)
MOVED WEDNESDAY.
