attend ceremony for grand opening of the new Gorbachev Library, is
invited in for an
</P>
<P>
   in-promptu meeting with Russian President Vladimir Putin. The
two know one another from the time that Turner put on the Goodwill
Games in St. Petersburg, Putin's hometown. Developing. (Coker, Cox
News Service).
</P>
