<SLUG> BC-CORRECTIVE-ADLITTLE-BOS </SLUG>
  
 (Eds.: Newspapers that used the Boston Globe story ADLITTLE-SPINOFF
(f) by Jerry Ackerman, which moved May 10, will wish to use the
following corrective.
<TEXT>
<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   A Boston Globe article about Arthur D. Little Inc.'s plan to
spin off its technology-based divisions into a public company
incorrectly identified the president and chief executive of the
Cambridge, Mass. research company. He is Lorenzo C. Lamadrid.
</P>
