Saturday is Keep Your Cat Indoors Day, the brainchild of the
American Bird Conservancy of Washington, D.C. Estimates are that
birds comprise about 20 percent of the diet of free-ranging cats,
both feral and domestic. By Erik Nelson. (Will move in the ``a''
national and ``n'' California news files.)
</P>
<P>
   X X X
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
