<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Thursday, 05/11/00. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been
posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   ANCIENT_Skull locator -- 1 x 3 1/4 -- SCI-ANCIENT-SKULL
</P>
<P>
   CZECH_Brno locator -- 1 x 2 1/4 -- CZECH-GYPSIES
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO_Landovica map -- 1 x 2 1/2 -- KOSOVO-UNREST
</P>
<P>
