<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-11 22:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2578 &Cx1f; ttf-z
u v BC-PHOTO-UPDATE-NYT     05-11 2263
