Juliana Hatfield is on a 21-store tour playing three live
performances a day over seven days. The whirlwind New England
Newbury Comics record store tour leads up to the release of two new
Juliana Hatfield CDs. Hatfield playing at the Newbury Comics record
store in Newton, Mass. (Suzanne Kreiter/Boston Globe Poto)
</P>
