Bordick wasn't born in Maine. He lived in Marquette, Mich., until
his family moved to Winterport as he was entering his sophomore
year in high school. But he learned how to play ball there and he
feels like a Maine guy, which is all that counts to Bordick and the
state of Maine. (Tom Herde/Boston Globe Photo)
</P>
